_______________________________________________________________________________
"Emotion Control"  
        This allows the psionicist to telepathically alter the emotions
        of creatures.  For a short time, it will make a peaceful monster
        aggressive, or an aggressive monster peaceful.  The monster's
        original attitude then returns.  Note that this is a GENERAL
        attitude change.  If the monster is already fighting someone, it
        won't stop fighting that particular character.  This is an
        unusual power that has many creative uses.  
 
SP Cost:  15		Guild Level:  10	Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  emotion <target>
